左人關心就跳樓，咁點解佢唔可以主動去公公屋探佢關心佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fe556867f16cf85ee3f838e345226d65a3b5a98","tid":1065674,"uid":51171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7bbb62f75e3a7fb6effb4ae01becca8e15a37e37","tid":1065674,"uid":174013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T12:05:13.000Z","msg":"睇完明白點解自殺未"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T12:09:24.000Z","msg":"未"},{"pid":"0cbf187465277fe38bbb9dc14f8db20c7fb8e008","tid":1065674,"uid":237969,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T12:09:29.000Z","msg":"單親媽老豆跳樓關個阿婆咩事？<br />\n我係咪睇漏嘢<br />\n<br />\n同埋點解佢老豆跳樓佢就唔搬<br />\n個邏輯係邊<br />\n講到阿婆堅恐怖但有得走唔走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99d53d64c014e20babb202ef5d26a5b96af321c8","tid":1065674,"uid":51171,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7bbb62f75e3a7fb6effb4ae01becca8e15a37e37","tid":1065674,"uid":174013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T12:05:13.000Z","msg":"睇完明白點解自殺未"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T12:11:17.000Z","msg":"跳樓嗰個係單親媽個老豆，住第二到的。<br />\n想問你睇完理解到點解佢老豆自殺未?"},{"pid":"15d5263e62a2a876aebae2f3c74c7816e44da4da","tid":1065674,"uid":187264,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T12:12:34.000Z","msg":"2邊都有問題<br />\n講到自己住得咁危險都拒絕搬新單位...就係因為有白事要做?<br />\n咪玩啦,單位唔啱心水吧"},{"pid":"bc557ea2012bb2e20125410eb11d2baeb4e37dea","tid":1065674,"uid":62195,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T12:13:27.000Z","msg":"有得走唔走<br />\n想留番係新公屋到<br />\n肯定派個到係舊邨唔岩心水<br />\n老豆死唔關事都拉埋黎講<br />\n啊婆有病還有病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8620e5aaea51355aa763658e1400d018b36036a8","tid":1065674,"uid":69681,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T12:14:08.000Z","msg":"被迫害妄想症"},{"pid":"7d7c29c7a80deb25561f3992e57a7b58f910363e","tid":1065674,"uid":65384,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T12:14:24.000Z","msg":"阿婆係真癲<br />\n但個單親媽都奇奇怪怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己老豆都唔係住果間屋<br />\n自殺死左又賴落阿婆到？<br />\n之前房署俾左新屋佢又唔要"},{"pid":"e537839fa29b1328ae23e970a4f1217072002543","tid":1065674,"uid":187264,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7d7c29c7a80deb25561f3992e57a7b58f910363e","tid":1065674,"uid":65384,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T12:14:24.000Z","msg":"阿婆係真癲<br />\n但個單親媽都奇奇怪怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己老豆都唔係住果間屋<br />\n自殺死左又賴落阿婆到？<br />\n之前房署俾左新屋佢又唔要"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T12:14:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5204dc4d636c652bf37efb625cb62745ac2f6b22","tid":1065674,"uid":24617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d7c29c7a80deb25561f3992e57a7b58f910363e","tid":1065674,"uid":65384,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T12:14:24.000Z","msg":"阿婆係真癲<br />\n但個單親媽都奇奇怪怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己老豆都唔係住果間屋<br />\n自殺死左又賴落阿婆到？<br />\n之前房署俾左新屋佢又唔要"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T12:21:52.000Z","msg":"佢講過話個阿婆成日見到佢老豆就話佢過唔到7月14<br />\n最後好似話7月14定7月14前自殺<br />\n不過都搞緊調遷<br />\n咪暫時搬去老豆到住一排<br />\n之後有派新屋又話搞白事唔要<br />\n而家後悔所以搵東張幫手睇下可唔可以派多次？"},{"pid":"95ce039cecc57135e07cb1bf9c98df901f174836","tid":1065674,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T12:22:52.000Z","msg":"阿婆跑得快"},{"pid":"9fda2a4f8edea99b55727e5658215b243ac7345b","tid":1065674,"uid":51171,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"e537839fa29b1328ae23e970a4f1217072002543","tid":1065674,"uid":187264,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7d7c29c7a80deb25561f3992e57a7b58f910363e","tid":1065674,"uid":65384,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T12:14:24.000Z","msg":"阿婆係真癲<br />\n但個單親媽都奇奇怪怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/no